## ğŸ” Task 1: Aspect Term Extraction (ATE)

<div align="center">

### ğŸ¯ **Goal**: Extract exact aspect terms from sentences

</div>

### ğŸ—ï¸ Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Input Sentence] --> B[Word Embeddings]
    B --> C[Bi-GRU/RNN]
    C --> D[Dense Layer]
    D --> E[BIO Tags]
    E --> F[Aspect Terms]
```

### âš™ï¸ Technical Specifications

| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **ğŸ§  Architecture** | Bidirectional GRU/RNN |
| **ğŸ“Š Embeddings** | GloVe 300D / fastText 300D |
| **ğŸ·ï¸ Tagging Scheme** | BIO (Beginning-Inside-Outside) |
| **ğŸ“‰ Loss Function** | CrossEntropyLoss with padding mask |
| **ğŸ“ Evaluation** | Chunk-level F1 Score (CoNLL eval) |

### ğŸ† Performance Results

<div align="center">

| Model | Embedding | Validation F1 | Status |
|-------|-----------|---------------|---------|
| **ğŸ¥‡ GRU** | **fastText** | **0.7165** | ğŸŒŸ **Best** |
| ğŸ¥ˆ GRU | GloVe | 0.7092 | â­ |
| ğŸ¥‰ RNN | fastText | 0.7013 | â­ |
| RNN | GloVe | 0.7000 | â­ |

**ğŸ¯ Final Test F1 Score: 0.7132**

</div>

