## ğŸ’­ Task 2: Aspect Sentiment Classification (ASC)

<div align="center">

### ğŸ¯ **Goal**: Predict sentiment for each extracted aspect

</div>

### ğŸ—ï¸ Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    A[Context + Aspect] --> B[GloVe Embeddings]
    B --> C[Bi-LSTM]
    C --> D[Aspect-Specific Attention]
    D --> E[Dense Layers]
    E --> F[4-Class Classification]
    F --> G[positive/negative/neutral/conflict]
```

### âš™ï¸ Technical Specifications

| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| **ğŸ§  Architecture** | Bi-LSTM + Aspect-Specific Attention |
| **ğŸ“Š Embeddings** | GloVe 300D |
| **ğŸ¯ Input Format** | Context tokens + aspect term indices |
| **ğŸ” Attention Mechanism** | Focuses on aspect-relevant context |
| **ğŸ“‰ Loss Function** | CrossEntropyLoss |
| **ğŸ“ Evaluation Metric** | Classification Accuracy |

### ğŸ† Performance Results

<div align="center">

| Metric | Score | Status |
|--------|-------|---------|
| **ğŸ¯ Validation Accuracy** | **65.23%** | ğŸŒŸ **Best** |
| **ğŸ“Š Test Accuracy** | **62.50%** | âœ… **Final** |

</div>

